  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.959,
    "endTime": 258.935,
    "text": "Thandiswa Mazwai: Hello everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.959,
    "endTime": 261.616,
    "text": "Thank you so much for having us here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.64,
    "endTime": 263.44,
    "text": "My name is Thandiswa Mazwai."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.32,
    "endTime": 269.2,
    "text": "I am a wild woman, a rebel singer, a conduit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.279,
    "endTime": 273.216,
    "text": "My music is about memory"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.24,
    "endTime": 278.36,
    "text": "and struggling between oppresion and freedom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.88,
    "endTime": 283.96,
    "text": "After over 20 years in South Africa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.12,
    "endTime": 286.52,
    "text": "we find ourselves as the black masses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.2,
    "endTime": 292.56,
    "text": "still suffering and fighting for our freedom and humanity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.88,
    "endTime": 298.48,
    "text": "This first song was called \"Iyeza\" which means \"medicine.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.24,
    "endTime": 303.24,
    "text": "Medicine for our madness, medicine for our rage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.76,
    "endTime": 308.376,
    "text": "This song we're doing now is called \"Zabalaza,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.4,
    "endTime": 310.2,
    "text": "and it means \"rebel.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.2,
    "endTime": 316.575,
    "text": "I'd like to dedicate this to the valiant student movement in South Africa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.6,
    "endTime": 318.81600000000003,
    "text": "who came up with the #FeesMustFall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.84,
    "endTime": 319.936,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.96,
    "endTime": 321.296,
    "text": "Rhodes Must Fall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.32,
    "endTime": 323.296,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.32,
    "endTime": 324.896,
    "text": "But more importantly,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.92,
    "endTime": 328.896,
    "text": "the new vigor that has been brought into the feminist movement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.92,
    "endTime": 331.44,
    "text": "so patriarchy must fall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.0,
    "endTime": 336.16,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.4,
    "endTime": 338.84,
    "text": "(Music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.52,
    "endTime": 348.79999999999995,
    "text": "Gogo bek' umthwalo"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.76,
    "endTime": 354.28,
    "text": "Kunin' uhlupheka?"
  },
  {
